content:
We've renamed DataRaptor to Omnistudio Data Mapper. You'll see the updated name in the feature name and labels in the OmniStudio designers, documentation, and Trailhead modules. We've made these changes in a way so that your implementations continue to work. The new name appears in OmniStudio Spring '24 release and later.

This change applies to all editions with OmniStudio licenses.
title: Salesforce Summer '24 Release Notes
